<s> Per my action of the 10 April face-to-face meeting [1], here is a proposal to clarify checkpoint 9.2 (issue 208).  </s>
<s> The Working Group felt that this checkpoint was intended to allow configuration of prompting (like all the other checkpoints), but the wording did not capture that.  </s>
<s> Here is a proposed clarification:  </s>
<s> 9.2 Prompt the user to confirm any form submission triggered indirectly,  </s>
<s> that is by any means other than the user activating an explicit form submit control.  </s>
<s> When configured to do so, prompt the user to confirm any form submission triggered indirectly, that is by any means other than the user activating an explicit form submit control.  </s>
